snippet.title: Justice Bear: Equinox trailer
snippet.description:
Join Bearnard on a run through Amber Town's burning streets to help his family in this free game for Android, PC, WebGL and more platforms soon. Find more info in: https://justicebear.com/equinox

Download for Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cr0ss.equinox

Download for iOS:
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/justice-bear-equinox/id1290860614
